data.description: Welcome Home! Nestled in Country Grove Subdivision on 2.47 acres is this Custom Built in 1995 by Mark Overholser. Two-story Colonial home offers 2900 sq' w additional 1400 sq' finished basement.  Six paneled solid poplar wood doors through out and lots of crown molding! Gorgeous hardwood floors in LR, DR, FR and Kitchen and breakfast area. Kitchen and breakfast area also offers cherry cabinetry with all the extras: slide out shelves, baking sheet, spice and trash cabinets. All appliances included. (refrigerator with cherry wood front).Host your holiday dinners in the spacious DR with bay window(fabulous view) then enjoy your guest sitting around the FP(one of three) in the spacious FR or in the beautiful sun room with Cathedral ceiling and wall to ceiling windows. Make your way to the second floor where you will find a magnificent Master Bedroom Suite! Complete with a FP! The builder did not slight the size of the remaining 3 bedrooms.  One actually has an additional 10x16 suite. The 10x8 utility room with built in cabinets is on the second floor for your convenience. The finished basement offers plenty of space for what ever activity of your families choice: pool, ping pong, games or movies. Outside you will find the 2+ attached garage with opener, a shed plus an outbuilding!
